description: Philadelphia Original Cream Cheese traces its roots back to 1872, and it has been the standard of high quality cream cheese ever since. Today, it is made with five simple ingredients and is perfect for adding creaminess to recipes. You already love it for cheesecakes and dips, but be sure to give it a try for making creamy pasta sauce, delectable no-bake desserts, rich soups and much more. Local dairy farmers near Beaver Dam, WI and Lowville, NY supply Philly with fresh milk, which we combine with real cream. The entire process from farm to creamery takes just six days. But we don't stop at farm fresh milk and real cream. We also never add artificial preservatives, flavors or dyes in any of our cream cheese spreads. So in the end, everything just seems a little bit better with the creamy taste of Philly.
name: Cream Cheese Loaf

description: Coconut milk is a creamy and flavorful liquid made from the meat of coconuts. It is a popular ingredient in many cuisines, particularly in Southeast Asian and Caribbean dishes. Coconut milk can be used in a wide variety of dishes, from curries and soups to smoothies and baked goods.

description: So you’re a barista? Perfect. This carton of Barista Edition Oatmilk is made from liquid oats which means it isn’t overly sweet or excessively ""heavy"". What it is, is fully foamable putting you in total control over the density and performance of your foam so you can showcase your latte art skillz, sorry we mean skills. Anyway, give it a try and see what you think.   So you’re not a barista? Also perfect. Just heat this Barista Edition Oatmilk in a container while giving it a whirl until it foams up nicely and then pour yourself a latte without cow’s milk. And if you don’t feel like a latte you might be happy to know that this product tastes just as amazing if you skip all the foaming and pour it right into your coffee or drink it straight out of the container or pour it on your granola or put it to work with your cooking skills. But let’s keep that between us non-baristas, okay?
name: Barista Oat Milk

description:
Crème fraîche is a luxurious and versatile dairy product that originated in France. It is made from high-quality cream that is fermented with a special culture, resulting in a tangy and rich taste that is similar to sour cream, but with a smoother texture. Our crème fraîche is made with all-natural ingredients, including fresh cream and live cultures. It is free from any additives or preservatives, ensuring that you get the purest and most delicious crème fraîche possible.
This creamy and silky dairy product is perfect for a wide range of culinary uses. It can be used as a topping for sweet or savory dishes, such as fruit, pies, and roasted vegetables. It can also be used as a substitute for sour cream, whipped cream, or mayonnaise, adding a tangy and decadent flavor to your recipes.

description: Crème fraîche is a luxurious and versatile dairy product that originated in France. It is made from high-quality cream that is fermented with a special culture, resulting in a tangy and rich taste that is similar to sour cream, but with a smoother texture. Our crème fraîche is made with all-natural ingredients, including fresh cream and live cultures. It is free from any additives or preservatives, ensuring that you get the purest and most delicious crème fraîche possible. This creamy and silky dairy product is perfect for a wide range of culinary uses. It can be used as a topping for sweet or savory dishes, such as fruit, pies, and roasted vegetables. description: Philadelphia Original Cream Cheese traces its roots back to 1872, and it has been the standard of high quality cream cheese ever since. So in the end, everything just seems a little bit better with the creamy taste of Philly.

So in the end, everything just seems a little bit better with the creamy taste of Philly.

Tourlami plant-based butters have been specifically designed for foodservice uses that compare in taste, texture, and functionality to the best dairy-based butters. description: Philadelphia Original Cream Cheese traces its roots back to 1872, and it has been the standard of high quality cream cheese ever since. Today, it is made with five simple ingredients and is perfect for adding creaminess to recipes. You already love it for cheesecakes and dips, but be sure to give it a try for making creamy pasta sauce, delectable no-bake desserts, rich soups and much more. Local dairy farmers near Beaver Dam, WI and Lowville, NY supply Philly with fresh milk, which we combine with real cream. The entire process from farm to creamery takes just six days. But we don't stop at farm fresh milk and real cream. We also never add artificial preservatives, flavors or dyes in any of our cream cheese spreads. So in the end, everything just seems a little bit better with the creamy taste of Philly.

description: Kerrygold Salted Butter is a luscious, golden spread crafted from the finest Irish dairy. Known for its unparalleled quality and taste, our butter is an indulgent delight that adds a touch of elegance to your culinary creations. Savor the rich, creamy flavor that has made Kerrygold a beloved household name around the world. Our butter begins with the freshest, high-quality milk from grass-fed cows that roam the picturesque, green pastures of Ireland. These happy, well-nourished cows produce a milk that is rich in nutrients and flavors, setting the stage for an exceptional butter. At Kerrygold, we combine time-honored traditions with modern techniques to create a smooth, luxurious butter that is perfect for spreading, cooking, and baking. Our master butter makers churn the cream slowly and carefully, preserving its delicate flavor while adding just the right amount of fine sea salt to enhance its natural taste.

description: JUST Egg Frozen Liquid is a plant-based egg substitute that is a delicious and healthy alternative to traditional eggs. Made from mung bean protein, this liquid egg substitute is vegan, gluten-free, and non-GMO, making it a versatile ingredient that can be used in a wide range of recipes. The JUST Egg Frozen Liquid is incredibly easy to use. Simply thaw the product in the refrigerator, and then pour it directly into a hot pan or use it as a key ingredient in baking or cooking. The liquid has a smooth and creamy texture that mimics the taste and texture of traditional eggs, making it perfect for omelets, scrambles, frittatas, and other egg-based dishes.
name: Just Egg Liquid
